              <li><span class="roadmap-feature-dot"></span>Partnerships with conservation groups</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <footer class="roadmap-footer">
      <div>
        <h3>Stay Updated</h3>
        <p>Follow our progress and be the first to know about new features and improvements to What Bird.</p>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
